<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v4" title="Q8_v4" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      En una cocina industrial se utiliza la siguiente ficha para preparar bandejas de pollo adobado:
      <br />"Ficha de adobo para bandejas de pollo"
      <br />Producción del día: 180 bandejas de pollo.
      <br />Ingredientes de adobo por bandeja:
      <br />• <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de taza de salsa de soya.
      <br />• <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de taza de agua.
    </p>
    <p>
      Si se considera que <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> taza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:math>, 
      
      ¿cuántos mL de salsa de soya se necesitan en total para preparar las 180 bandejas?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">21 600 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La salsa de soya por bandeja es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn></m:math> mL. Para 180 bandejas se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, 21 600 mL no corresponde a la cantidad total de salsa de soya.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">14 400 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La salsa de soya por bandeja es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn></m:math> mL. Entonces, para 180 bandejas se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:math> mL de salsa de soya.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">36 000 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La salsa de soya por bandeja es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn></m:math> mL. Para 180 bandejas, el total es <m:math><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:math> mL. Como <m:math><m:mn>36&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:math>, esa opción no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">4 800 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La salsa de soya por bandeja es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn></m:math> mL. Para 180 bandejas se requiere <m:math><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:math> mL. Como <m:math><m:mn>4800</m:mn><m:mo>&lt;</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:math>, 4 800 mL no alcanza para preparar todas las bandejas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular cuántos mL de salsa de soya lleva una bandeja</strong></p>
            <p>Cada bandeja usa <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de taza de salsa de soya.</p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> taza</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mtext> mL</m:mtext></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>240</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn></m:math> mL.</p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, una bandeja necesita 80 mL de salsa de soya.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar por la cantidad de bandejas</strong></p>
            <p>Se preparan 180 bandejas, así que el total de salsa de soya es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>180</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14&#160;400</m:mn></m:math> mL.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La cantidad total obtenida es 14 400 mL.</p>
            <p>Esa cantidad corresponde a la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Se necesitan <strong>14 400 mL de salsa de soya</strong> para preparar las 180 bandejas.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>